headline: Hyatt Has Room for Improvement. The Stock Is a Buy.
summary: While Marriott and Hilton have largely transitioned to this model, Hyatt is in the midst of its transformation, meaning there’s more upside for investors.  Its recent sale of its Playa Hotel & Resorts is the latest example that Hyatt is successfully moving forward with this strategy, which will increasingly pay off in the coming years.  Hyatt  Hotels is doing something about it.
